Description:
   Interior Discipline is a Pugilist technique that harnesses internal energy
   to deliver a powerful focused strike. The fighter channels their internal
   training into a single devastating blow, targeting the opponent's core
   or internal organs to cause maximum disruption.

   The technique is derived from pressure-point fighting methods that focus
   on disrupting the opponent's internal alignment rather than simply
   delivering surface damage. A successful Interior Discipline strike can
   impair the target's regeneration or reduce their combat effectiveness
   as their body struggles to compensate for the internal impact. The
   focus required means this skill has a longer cooldown than basic attacks.
